44. Bf5 Kb7 45. Rg4 Nh5 46. Rg6 Nf4 47. Rh6 Ne2 {1/2-1/2 Corrales Jimenez,
F-Tang,A/Denver 2019/CBM 190 Extra}) (10. Qe4 $2 {many people will do this ...
but it seems that white has mixed things up !} O-O-O $15 {We protect the
bishop with our king and, at some moment, we will play c5 with tempo.} 11. Be3
(11. Bd3 $6 c5 (11... Re8 $17 {even this is much better for Black.}) 12. Qe2 ({
